Description: offers support for heterogeneous multicore architecture
Version: @PACKAGE_VERSION@
Cflags: -I${includedir}/starpu/@STARPU_EFFECTIVE_VERSION@ @STARPU_CUDA_CPPFLAGS@ @SIMGRID_CFLAGS@
